{"tid":1781221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新區議員想請人入","createTime":"2019-12-13T03:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:12:10.000Z","uid":54270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f40ef614159e2abd5656330a082158d4e456556b","tid":1781221,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"區軒都講過，對家開始出手，尤其係扮手足攞料。<br />\n不過大家請人第一關隨時出事比對家有位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請人呢<br />\n1.唔可以請自己親戚<br />\n2.唔可以圍標，一定要公開ad<br />\n咁樣申請津貼就會犯法，議員做到晒但自己係咪食血饅頭就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，個ad係唔可以話被捕手足優先鄺議員已經暗示過<br />\n<br />\n因為咁出ad其實自己犯咗<span style=\"color: red;\">直接歧視</span>，手足唔係合理競爭條件，<span style=\"color: red;\">客觀睇係唔公平</span>，記得係話不拘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a46c9bb9571acefea5d4000ae1cf667f924656","tid":1781221,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ef297cc3bd97d490cb14febbdafa4a6873ea92","tid":1781221,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6331108609105cc56086ad6df9abba25dd4847","tid":1781221,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2882de2f5be0b6e7934d65964121944b96d867ac","tid":1781221,"